high_descs: Turn around and go towards the sink, then go right, left, and left again into the bathroom.
Pick up the cookie from the sink.
Exit the room the way you came in, going straight against the wall, then right to the coffeetable.
Place the cookie on the coffeetable.
Turn right and go towards the kitchen area, to the microwave.
Remove the cookie from inside the microwave.
Return to the coffeetable where you put down the first bag of chips.
Place the second cookie on the coffeetable.
anns.task_desc: Place two bags of cookies on a coffee table.

high_descs: Enter the room. Enter the bathroom. Turn right next to the sink. Turn right.
Pick up the cookie that is in the sink.
Turn around. Continue to the coffeetable. Turn to the coffeetable and approach.
Place the cookie on the right side near the far corner of the coffeetable.
Turn around. Go to the microwave.
Open the microwave. Take the cookie bag. Close the microwave.
Return to the coffeetable.
Place the cookie bag before the coffeetable.
anns.task_desc: Find a cookie and a bag. Place them on a CoffeeTable.
